{"word":"ἄγρυπνος","slug":"ἄγρυπνος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἄγρυπνος</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἀγρέω'><el>ἀγρέω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>hunting after sleep</i>, <a href='S:id est'>i. e.</a> <i>sleepless, wakeful</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>: <a href='S:metaphorically'>metaph.</a>, <el>Ζηνὸς ἄγρ. βέλος</el> <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>; <el>τὸ ἄγρυπνον  ἀγρυπνία</el>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:active signification'><a href='S:Active voice'>act.</a></a> <i>keeping awake</i>, <el>μέριμναι</el> <b><a href='S:Anthology'>Anth.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}